#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-13-terminal-shortcuts.rst:7
msgid "Windows Terminal の便利操作集"
msgstr "Collection of useful operations for Windows Terminal"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-13-terminal-shortcuts.rst:9
msgid ""
"Windows Terminal 上での操作は、シェルの種類に関わらず共通して使えるものが多く、習得しておくと非常に効率が上がります。 "
"特に便利なものは意識的に使って体にしみ込ませてしまいたいものですが、使わないと忘れてしまうのでまとめておきます。"
msgstr ""
"Many operations on Windows Terminal can be used in common regardless of the "
"type of shell, and learning them will greatly improve your efficiency. You "
"want to consciously use things that are especially useful and let them soak "
"into your body, but if you don't use them, you'll forget them, so I've "
"summarized them here."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-13-terminal-shortcuts.rst:17
msgid "行頭・行末ジャンプ操作"
msgstr "Start/end of line jump operation"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-13-terminal-shortcuts.rst:19
msgid "以下の操作は、bash、zsh、PowerShell など多くのシェルで共通して使えるものです（Emacs風キーバインド）。"
msgstr ""
"The following operations can be used commonly in many shells such as bash, "
"zsh, and PowerShell (Emacs-style key bindings)."

